{"tid":2011876,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"從腳傷理解殘疾人士之苦","createTime":"2020-05-11T09:43:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-11T10:45:25.000Z","uid":308377,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"90faf6efc4841585d6015b0e71ce3fd983f225a3","tid":2011876,"uid":308377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T09:43:06.000Z","msg":"話說一個月前叉錯腳搞到扭傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n出世到而家極少整親隻腳<br />\n頭兩星期行兩步都痛到懷疑人生<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n特別係啱啱整親果日果幾個鐘<br />\n真係好辛苦<br />\n頂住痛楚轉兩程車番屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一轉二程車係尖沙咀<br />\n要通過一條長隨道過對面<br />\n我實在痛到唔點行到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n扶住牆拖住隻腳半爬過去<br />\n沿途有好多人經過<br />\n冇人理我（其實冇所謂，我已經慣咗港豬嘅冷血）<br />\n好彩有少少扶手可以借力<br />\n不至於要係地下爬過去<br />\n幾經辛苦終於番到屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以前成日聽到殘疾人士話社會對佢哋唔友善<br />\n無障礙設施不足<br />\n呢一個月我充份感受到真係好差<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔通殘疾人士冇人權？<br />\n個個人都想自己有病嫁咩？<br />\n當然有啲過分要求福利嘅真係太貪心<br />\n但依加連基本想行路都難<br />\n<br />\n呢個政府完全係廢嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咩都做唔到<br />\n連基本建設都係成督屎禁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n更何況政治層面<br />\n<br />\n可能睇到呢度大家都冇乜感覺<br />\n但試想一日自己有需要用到時<br />\n會有咩感覺<br />\n<br />\n多謝你，睇曬篇文。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae46ddec369c10ab0a74ce8dbf5991060422eabd","tid":2011876,"uid":42751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T09:46:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d30a1db47784d7a31000201f38567b9314c0d538","tid":2011876,"uid":308377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae46ddec369c10ab0a74ce8dbf5991060422eabd","tid":2011876,"uid":42751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T09:46:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T10:45:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}